# CLAUDE.md

This is a generated blank Mantle site. Start from:

1. [`.mantle/launch-state.json`](.mantle/launch-state.json)
2. [`.mantle/features.json`](.mantle/features.json)
3. [`.mantle/handoff.md`](.mantle/handoff.md)
4. [`AGENTS.md`](AGENTS.md)

Repo-local skills:

- `.claude/skills/mantle-develop/SKILL.md`
- `.claude/skills/mantle-theme/SKILL.md`
- `.claude/skills/mantle-update/SKILL.md`

The launch archetype bundle is already applied. Inspect the generated
manifest, overlay notes, and seed prompt before changing code; do not
switch to an old full starter or a first-run theme.

Local checks:

```bash
pnpm install --frozen-lockfile
pnpm check
```

Use Claude Code for ongoing site maintenance, especially media uploads.
R2-backed media is optional post-launch work and may require Cloudflare
billing or a credit card. If media is needed, read
`node_modules/@aotter/mantle/docs/media-uploads.md` or
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aotter/mantle/develop/docs/media-uploads.md.
Claude Cowork usually cannot complete the R2 PUT step unless
`*.r2.cloudflarestorage.com` is allowlisted for egress.
